00:11:19.308 --> 00:11:20.849
Kur ju jeni drita,

00:11:21.308 --> 00:11:23.891
atehere ne kete drite ju mund te shihni lehtesisht

00:11:24.225 --> 00:11:26.724
si punon mendja juaj,

00:11:27.225 --> 00:11:29.308
cfare idesh ju jep,

00:11:29.683 --> 00:11:36.225
cfare ndikon tek mendja juaj

00:11:36.933 --> 00:11:38.891
ndersa ju po ngriheni.

00:11:39.225 --> 00:11:41.141
Eshte ky shqetesimi

00:11:41.433 --> 00:11:46.933
apo eshte kjo pergjegjesia qe keni?

00:11:47.308 --> 00:11:51.558
Ose eshte kjo prej zakoneve te keqija qe keni patur,

00:11:51.974 --> 00:11:53.724
qe ka nje pengese

00:11:54.100 --> 00:11:59.225
ne rritjen tuaj si nje personalitet shpirteror?

00:11:59.933 --> 00:12:02.682
Pra ju duhet te ruani veten gjate gjithe kohes,

00:12:03.058 --> 00:12:08.058
