00:13:08.100 --> 00:13:12.724
Nese ju zhvilloni nje ide te tille egoistike,

00:13:13.225 --> 00:13:15.891
nuk ka per t'ju ndihmuar aspak.

00:13:16.392 --> 00:13:19.392
Ajo qe ju duhet te beni eshte te 

00:13:20.183 --> 00:13:22.016
beni introspektive ndaj vetes gjithe kohes.

00:13:22.433 --> 00:13:24.600
Per kete eshte meditimi,

00:13:24.974 --> 00:13:26.517
te shihni per veten

00:13:26.849 --> 00:13:30.974
si po e mbani lart

00:13:31.475 --> 00:13:34.642
ngritjen tuaj shpirterore.

00:13:35.141 --> 00:13:36.558
Askush tjeter s'mund ta beje,

00:13:36.974 --> 00:13:39.392
